        "content": "<p>Hello, </p>\n<p>I need help proving the following Lemma. The lemma tries to prove that every prime &gt; 3 is not divisible by 2. An elementally task for a seasoned Leaner!  </p>\n<p>lemma theo1 (p : ℕ) (hp : p &gt; 3) (hprime : Nat.Prime p) : ¬ (2 ∣ p) := by</p>",
